prodNameC: 瑟若汀 英孚洛爾卓定康試驗系統
ingredientsDesc:
The reagent set is sufficient for 150 tests and consists of the following reragents:
1. CerticanR Antibody Reagent (5 mL); <5% rabbit antisera in buffer containing protein as stabilizer and <0.1% sodium azide as preservative. Vial cap label “A”.
2. CerticanR Tracer Reagent (5 mL); <1% fluorescein tracer in buffer containing protein as stabilizer, a surfactant, and <0.1% sodium azide as preservative. Vial cap labeled “T”.
3. CerticanR Pretreatment Buffer (5 mL); tris buffer, detergent, and <0.1% sodium azide as preservative. Vial cap labeled “B”.
4. Precipitation Reagent (7.5 mL); containing precipitating reagent, and <0.1% sodium azide.
